text: Gizela Niedurny (born 31 January 1939) is a Polish gymnast. She competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ruda Śląska
